// =============================================
// SECTION 4: Flowcharts and Diagrams
// =============================================

### Flowcharts and Process Diagrams

::: grid FlowGrid cols=2 gap=24
  ::: card ApprovalFlowCard
    ### Approval Pipeline
    ::: flowchart ApprovalProcess
      Start (circle)
      Submit (rect)
      Review (diamond)
      Approved (diamond)
      Deploy (rect)
      End (circle)

      Start -> Submit
      Submit -> Review
      Review -> Approved: Pass
      Review -> Submit: Reject
      Approved -> Deploy
      Deploy -> End
    :::
  :::

  ::: card DevOpsFlowCard
    ### DevOps Pipeline
    ::: flowchart CICDPipeline
      Code (rect)
      Build (rect)
      Test (diamond)
      Stage (rect)
      Prod (circle)

      Code -> Build
      Build -> Test
      Test -> Stage: Pass
      Test -> Code: Fail
      Stage -> Prod
    :::
  :::
:::

