---

### Document Footer

This document demonstrates every element supported by the Slate markup language.

- Typography: titles, subtitles, headings, paragraphs, lists, blockquotes, checkboxes
- Layout: sections, grids, cards, rows, spacers, dividers
- Data: stat panels, bar charts, line charts, pie charts, donut charts
- Diagrams: flowcharts with rect, circle, diamond nodes and labeled edges
- Forms: text inputs, email fields, password fields, select dropdowns, submit buttons

> Slate compiles to structured JSON and renders natively through the slate.js engine.
